shepherding
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:(in rugby) the illegal shielding of a player with the ball; the illegal obstruction of an opponent from tackling the player with the ball
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
